name: Farmers Market
team: Hannah Tran, Varsha Jawadi, Alice Lan, Romy
description: Contains About the farmer's market, Directions, Featured food vendors, Event Schedule, Links, RSVP form, image gallery that you can click through to select images to zoom in. Unfortunately the nav bar and buttons don't lead anywhere

name: RSVPortal
team: Cailey Murad, Loreen Samaan, Khuyen Lai, and Kumiko Komori
description: RSVPortal is a web application that aims to be a centeralized platform for UCSD events! UCSD students can post and discover events, from club meetups to study sessions.

name: Moondance
description: This is an event website showcasing a fictional film festival. It features a carousel with images of the movies that would be screened at the festival and a functional RSVP connected to Formspree.

name: Diamond Dash
description: Diamond Dash is a 24-hour Minecraft mining challenge for UCSD students. Players compete to mine the most diamonds before the server closes. Key Features: live Minecraft survival server (24 hours), PvP with real-world rewards, top 3 players win exclusive prizes, and built-in player compass for tracking other players. In the website you can learn the rules, RSVP for the event, view the schedule, and view prizes.

name: Preserving San Diego
team: Stephanie Yan, Nikita Jos, Serina Wang, Simar Gowda, Sharon Ma, Tanya Sinha
description: A website that educates and encourages its visitors to participate in local efforts toward preserving the beauty and history of San Diego's natural ecosystems.

name: Light Polution
team: Akari Oh, Anagha Kamath, Gayathri Kuniyil, Himansi Gupta, Katherine Charry
description: This is an educational website aimed at raising awareness about light pollution, its causes, and its effects on both the environment and human health. It provides an interactive platform where users can learn about light pollution through visual aids, interactive elements, and detailed explanations.

name: Shop Local
team: Esha Shah, Cameryn Mogul, Shruti Senthilram
description: 'Shop Local, San Diego' is a website highlighting local businesses in San Diego, encouraging community support of small shops and restaurants. The site features a clean, eco-themed design with smooth animations and mobile responsiveness.

name: Sustainable Living
team: Kyla Ma, Perla Ramirez, Joy Liu, Sophia Hernandez
description: Our website is about sustainable living. We want to teach people about what we eat, what waste we produce, and how to reduce it. Explore our website to see where you stand and join our cause!

name: Triton Wayfinder
team: Hoang Dung Tran, Sydney Su, Khuyen Lai, Anna Pak
description: Our website is for UCSD students, visitors, and guests to help them navigate through and around campus
